svg.text: This one is a svg copy of the original parts
provided as pngs in the pack
This is my own custom breakdown of the original
parts with the intention of being able to be used
to make solid animations without relying on mesh
because robots are made of metal I thought it would look best
if the robot was animated without using mesh morphing so I
created a set of parts that provide the necessary number of bones
to create decent animations without mesh morphing
These are different robot weapon upgades
